{"word":"Ahithophel","slug":"ahithophel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahithophel</b> <a href=\"#/H302\">H302</a> <br/> One of David's counsellors<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=12'>2Sa 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=33'>1Ch 27:33</a><br/> Joins Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=31'>2Sa 15:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=34'>2Sa 15:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=15'>2Sa 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=23'>2Sa 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=23'>2Sa 17:23</a><br/> Probably referred to by David in Psalm 55,12-14<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=55&verse=14'>Psa 55:14</a><br/> Suicide of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=14'>2Sa 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=23'>2Sa 17:23</a>"}]}